    "Depending on the context, insightfulness and correctness might have different importance.",
    "We define the weighting factor α in the resulting function.",
    "The objective is to maximize the weighted harmonic mean:",
    "By default, we assign insightfulness and correctness the same importance (α = 0.5).",
